title: Space Puzzle v1.2
description:
This paid version of Space Puzzle contains 40 levels. Before you buy, try the free Space Puzzle Lite which comes with 20 levels.

Intellijoy's MissinGames division is pleased to announce the launch of Space Puzzle, a brainy game for both parents and kids.
The object of the Space Puzzle is simple.

Given a limited number of wall-to-wall moves, help Intellibuzz reach the Space Station. While at it, collect as many stars as you can.
Space Puzzle game will improve your and your child's spatial logic skills and encourage anticipative thinking.

What's New:

Bug fixes.
